                        <item xml:id="e1">- The Ms. is foliated twice, at the top and bottom margins.&#xD;
- An extensive passage of the text was erased: fol. 19ra.&#xD;
- Names, like Gäbrä Mädḫǝn, Gäbrä Mukaʾel, Wälättä Krǝstosare, are written in pencil on some fols.: 18r, 104vb, 109v.&#xD;
- Compressed script: fols. 26va-27va, 45ra-45va, 57ra-va, 83vb-84ra.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 15va, 17va, 18vb, 34va, 42vb, 43ra, 44ra, 45va, 56va, 59ra, 63vb, 103ra.&#xD;
- Spaces for rubricated names left unfilled or names erased from the supplication formula and filled with horizontal lines: e.g., fols. 18vb, 20rb, 20vb, 21rb-vb, 22va, 28rb, 28va, 31va, 33ra-vb, 34ra, 42va, 43ra, 44ra, 46vb, 47ra, 48vb, 49ra.</item>
